</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E1150D16A3FCFF54AEBDE5D329E4FB1B" blockId="178.[189,1398,1156,1218]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">
This species is named in honor of Dr. Rauno E. Linnavuori, author of 5 valid tribes, 2 subtribes, 127 genera and 671 species of 
<taxonomicName id="26AA7695A3FCFF54AFF3E5FF29E8FB1B" baseAuthorityName="Zahniser &amp; Dietrich" baseAuthorityYear="2010" box="[499,694,1192,1218]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="178" pageNumber="179" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subFamily" subFamily="Deltocephalinae">Deltocephalinae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
